                    <h4>- John Doe, Recipient</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <img src="images/team-2.jpg" alt="Testimonial 2">
                    <p>"Being a part of this mission as a donor is so fulfilling. Knowing I’m making a difference keeps me coming back to support new drives."</p>
                    <h4>- Jane Smith, Donor</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial">
                    <img src="images/team-1.jpg" alt="Testimonial 3">
                    <p>"Coordinating the logistics for donation drives is challenging but rewarding. It’s amazing to see how much we can achieve together."</p>
                    <h4>- Mike Johnson, Logistics Coordinator</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="cta-section impact-page">
        <div class="container">
            <h3>Be Part of the Change</h3>
            <p>Whether you donate, volunteer, or help organize, your contribution matters. Join us in making an impact!</p>
            <a href="#" class="get-involved-btn">Get Involved</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
